{"tid":642143,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【巨胸再現】開完演唱會後唔敢喪食 乳酪頂肚","createTime":"2018-04-25T14:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T12:28:31.000Z","uid":100150,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"01464803daf5885f4f7d65ddf1e305978d3361a5","tid":642143,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524654928_a8b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524654928_a8b3.jpg&h=7d022a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n欣宜開完演唱會，就約埋一班朋友去游水，happy一下。(ig圖片/資料圖片)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n鄭欣宜（Joyce）剛完成兩場紅館處女騷，當然可以放鬆心情，約埋朋友一齊慶祝一吓。噚日Joyce就喺ig story上載游水短片，佢着住一條黑白間條泳衣，向來擁有勁爆身材嘅Joyce，亦唔介意喺鏡頭前晒巨胸，一邊歎住特飲一邊自拍，非常開心。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJoyce同一班朋友仲相約去食lunch，Joyce冇因為開完騷而放肆任食，反而擇咗較清淡嘅乳酪，佢話﹕「嘩，你哋食啲咁heavy嘅嘢，睇我幾乖，我食Yogurt咋。」朋友見佢咁慘豬，即刻拎咗一個生果蛋糕畀佢，唔知Joyce最後抵唔抵受得住誘惑呢？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524654930_bc28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524654930_bc28.jpg&h=4d205ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n欣宜再晒巨胸。(ig圖片)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524654932_9250.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524654932_9250.jpg&h=97b12aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n(ig圖片)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524654933_4a47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524654933_4a47.jpg&h=ce2e9e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n欣宜只係食乳酪。(ig圖片)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524654935_b9e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524654935_b9e7.jpg&h=312ac54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n欣宜啲朋友見佢咁慘，即時遞上美味蛋糕。(ig圖片)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180425/58117640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58117640&d=OKkKX4yRVxIvfeGBdKyXJZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=637cd4b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58117640&h=4f8e3136\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180425/58117640</a>"},{"pid":"ec6228f9f2abdf05da8cfb24331f6eec2fbdcbc2","tid":642143,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df6361b3c2bfa744fb8fd5147a78823f70bd711","tid":642143,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"btw俾左正評"},{"pid":"c1c11fc9770689690161b419f9c74ee46a57e08e","tid":642143,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:16:02.000Z","msg":"屌你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24028c680f9194103eb58eb01187887d73bd5b84","tid":642143,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:17:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"847d17f76cc1fff7e6e7cc08a4a9c1cc2c51ac2e","tid":642143,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"屌⋯ 第一張隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高難度動作"},{"pid":"125d71dd01a7535bb1d3df9f7480d0a7036d97dc","tid":642143,"uid":87757,"like":1,"disl